  <brief_title>Magnet Resonance Imaging to Evaluate of Dynamic T2 Preparation Puls by Patients With Shunt or Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cardiac Magnet Resonance Imaging to Evaluate of Dynamic T2 Preparation Puls by Patient With Shunt or Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)</official_title>
